  "In Separate mode, this is the full API response. In Together mode, this is the extracted JSON block that was stripped from the AI's narrative response.": "W Oddzielnym — pełna odpowiedź. W Razem — wyodrębniony JSON.",
  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "AI pisze odpowiedź i dodaje JSON. ScenePulse wyodrębnia i ukrywa.",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "Jeśli AI pominie, ScenePulse może odzyskać automatycznie. Wymaga profilu.",
